---
title: Babagahummus with Parsley & Chilli | Serves 2
description: Get ready to dip, spread, and scoop with this smokey, eggplant-based dip! This creamy combo of babaganoush and zesty hummus is packed with bold flavours. Fresh parsley adds a pop of green, and a hint of chili brings just the right kick. Perfect for snacks, party platters, or jazzing up your meals—it's the duo you didn’t know you needed!
